        },
        "text_PJxJEe": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>You received The World because a significant chapter of your life is complete, even if you haven’t formally named it yet. This card often appears for people who are already thinking ahead, planning the next step, or searching for what comes next, without fully acknowledging how much they’ve already integrated.<\/p><p>The World comes when lessons have been learned, cycles have closed, and identity has stabilised. You may notice that situations that once challenged you no longer hold the same emotional charge. You just respond differently now, and it matters.<\/p><p>This card chooses people who are ready to stop proving and start embodying. You’ve grown into a version of yourself that no longer needs constant validation, urgency, or comparison.<\/p><p>You received this card because it’s time to pause and recognise wholeness before beginning again. Without this pause, you risk carrying old patterns into new chapters unnecessarily. The World reminds you that completion is sacred, and this process deserves acknowledgement, rest, and sometimes even celebration.<\/p><p>This card doesn’t rush you forward. What comes next will be chosen from stability.<br\/><br\/>On Love<\/p><p>Love is reaching maturity. This could mean strong commitment, long-term clarity, or a much needed emotional closure that could finally bring you the peace you were looking for. <\/p><h3>On Health<\/h3><p>Your body finds balance after years of adjustment. You feel more at home with and in yourself.<\/p><h3>On Money \/ Career<\/h3><p>There could be recognition or completion of a long-term product. You are either graduating from a role or identity you have outgrown. <\/p><h3>How to work with this energy<\/h3><p>Celebrate! Mark your endings with pride and intention. Rest, and when you start again, do so confidently.  <\/p><h3>Recommended products<\/h3><ol><li>Sunday Rituals Hair Repair & Growth Oil – Sealing cycles, honouring the journey<br\/><\/li><li>Rose Apple Bag Charm (Apple) – Abundance & completion<br\/><\/li><li>Enamel pin (Blue lupine) – Creativity & new possibilities<br\/><\/li><\/ol><p>You can find these in our pop-up booth at Night At Orchard, along the outdoor pathway between Ngee Ann City & Ion Orchard between 26-28 Dec, 3pm onwards <\/p>",
            "text_size": "typeset2",
            "secondary_color": false,
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        },
